reviewText: My 5 yr. old son is a very big fan of Wonder Pets and ever since it got removed from Netflix, he was very sad. This DVD brought back his smile and his younger sister is also slowly becoming a fan. I myself enjoy the cartoon with them and Ming Ming is our favorite. The concept of the cartoon is very simple and enjoyable for the children.

reviewText: For the past few months, my favorite TV shows have been House and Wonderpets.  All Wonderpets episodes are practically the same, so it doesn't really matter which DVD you get.  My fiance's son loves this series and I do too.  So much effort is put into the music and animation, and it always makes me laugh.
